Package: fmpbrunch
Title: Lightweight Client for FinancialModelingPrep (v3 and Stable)
Version: 0.4.7
Authors@R: c(
    person("Börsenbrunch", family = "", email = "boersenbrunch@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Lightweight R client for FinancialModelingPrep. Supports prices,
    metrics, profiles, news, quotes, screeners, and bulk CSV endpoints across
    v3 and stable APIs. Returns tidy tibbles with harmonized columns where
    possible.
